data.description: Own a slice of urban paradise in this captivating 2-bedroom, 1-bathroom haven in Indianapolis. Infused with modern charm and effortless style, this residence offers a retreat from the bustling city. The well-equipped chef's kitchen, complete with granite counters and a wine fridge, inspires culinary creativity. Rejuvenate your senses in the spa-like bathroom, offering a tranquil escape. Seamlessly manage your home with the smart feature intercom system, ensuring convenience at your fingertips. Step outdoors to your private oasis, a backyard sanctuary enveloped by a fence. Embrace the exquisite essence of the Fountain Square subdivision with this remarkable abode.
